It’s officially bbq szn & that means lots of pasta salad to go with it! I know it sounds kind of weird, but mixing Pace Pincante sauce with Italian Dressing, makes the best pasta salad! You’re going to have to just go for it & trust me on this one🙌🏻 

How I make it:

1 box of rotini pasta (cook al dente and rinse with cool water when finished), next, add in your fav pasta salad fixings! We love bell peppers, broccoli, tomatoes, black olives, salami, and cubed cheese

Add 1/2 a jar of Pace Picante Mild sauce and 1/2 a bottle of Italian dressing. Mix together and chill before serving. Add a little more salsa & Italian dressing to coat the pasta salad before serving!
